  "detailed_description": "<h1>Collector's Edition</h1><p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>\t30 scene locations<br></li><li>\t20 Achievements to earn</li></ul></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1>Explore beautiful locations spanning the Western states as you hunt for hidden objects. Hidden Object enthusiasts will rejoice with over 2,200 objects to locate across multiple game modes and beautiful hi-resolution scenes! For a change of pace, test your puzzle solving skills against a fun selection of 7 mini games! Don’t miss this trip of a lifetime!<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>\tTest your US trivia in the finale<br></li><li>\tMultiple search modes – Riddle, Alpha Sort, Scramble, Missing Vowels, and Silhouette<br></li><li>\tFind all the robots to unlock bonus puzzles<br></li><li>\tFind Max, Bear and Ninja the Max the Cat Studio Cats for extra points!</li></ul><br>Includes multiple levels of puzzles, increasing in challenge.<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>\tMatch Three<br></li><li>\tMahjong<br></li><li>\tJigsaw<br></li><li>\tTile Slide<br></li><li>\tBlock Slide<br></li><li>\tSpot the Difference<br></li><li>\tSolitaire</li></ul><br>Play how you want, adjust settings to your desire to match your playing ability or style.",
  "about_the_game": "Explore beautiful locations spanning the Western states as you hunt for hidden objects. Hidden Object enthusiasts will rejoice with over 2,200 objects to locate across multiple game modes and beautiful hi-resolution scenes! For a change of pace, test your puzzle solving skills against a fun selection of 7 mini games! Don’t miss this trip of a lifetime!<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>\tTest your US trivia in the finale<br></li><li>\tMultiple search modes – Riddle, Alpha Sort, Scramble, Missing Vowels, and Silhouette<br></li><li>\tFind all the robots to unlock bonus puzzles<br></li><li>\tFind Max, Bear and Ninja the Max the Cat Studio Cats for extra points!</li></ul><br>Includes multiple levels of puzzles, increasing in challenge.<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>\tMatch Three<br></li><li>\tMahjong<br></li><li>\tJigsaw<br></li><li>\tTile Slide<br></li><li>\tBlock Slide<br></li><li>\tSpot the Difference<br></li><li>\tSolitaire</li></ul><br>Play how you want, adjust settings to your desire to match your playing ability or style.",
